    "title": "商业模式的“克制与激进”",
    "page_range": "1",
    "summary": "**Topics:** Game monetization strategy, long-term sustainability vs. short-term revenue, player experience fairness, open-world/wuxia design philosophy.\n**Entities:** 《燕云十六声》 (game title), 点点数据 (data analytics firm), 项目组/厂商 (developers/project team), 玩家 (players).\n**Dates:** None mentioned.\n**Definitions:** “纯外观付费”模式 (monetization strictly limited to cosmetic items, explicitly excluding numerical/stat advantages); “数值枷锁” (pay-to-win mechanics where spending directly impacts gameplay balance or character power).\n**Procedures:** None described.\n**Claims:** Adopting a cosmetic-only model intentionally sacrifices short-term revenue spikes, shifting profitability to long-term player emotional and content attachment; removing numerical advantages ensures fair core experiences for all players, preserving open-world exploration and wuxia immersion purity; this approach is jointly recognized by players and developers as the fundamental driver of the game's long-term vitality.\n**Metrics:** Active user count and commercial performance (both exceeded the project team's original expectations).\n**Evidence Types:** Third-party market data verification (Diandian Data cross-referencing multiple sources), stakeholder consensus (players and developers).\n**Tables/Figures:** None present."
  },
  {
    "node_id": "0106",
    "title": "游戏玩法的“危险融合”",
    "page_range": "1",
    "summary": "This section answers questions regarding the gameplay design philosophy, development challenges, and iterative updates for 《燕云十六声》. It defines the “危险融合” (dangerous fusion) model as a hybrid of single-player immersive experience and multiplayer social elements, and defines the “江湖” (jianghu) concept as encompassing both solitary cultivation and factional cooperation/conflict. Key claims address the model’s high design complexity, tuning costs, and risk in satisfying divergent single-player and online player expectations, alongside initial player criticism of an “awkward” experience due to immature early design. Documented procedures for refinement include optimizing multiplayer interactions and introducing friend co-building home social features. Evidence is derived from player community feedback and developer design rationale. The section contains no specific dates, quantitative metrics, tables, or figures."
  },
