    "title": "基于项目组擅长品类精准挖掘出“轻度MMO”的细分蓝海赛道",
    "page_range": "33",
    "summary": "This section answers retrieval queries regarding the strategic positioning, design mechanics, and commercial impact of the game 《杖剑传说》.\n- **Topics:** Game genre hybridization, market segmentation (\"blue ocean\"), target demographic profiling, and revenue attribution.\n- **Entities:** 《杖剑传说》 (game title), 厦门吉比特网络技术股份有限公司 (G-bits Network Technology), “轻度MMO” (Light MMO), 放置游戏 (Idle games), 传统MMO手游 (Traditional MMO mobile games).\n- **Dates:** Q3 2025 (2025年第三季度).\n- **Definitions:** “轻度MMO” is defined as a hybrid model built on an idle game’s minimalist framework that deeply integrates core MMO social and progression systems, designed to reduce player burden while maintaining long-term engagement depth.\n- **Procedures/Design Features:** Systematic integration of MMO mechanics (group dungeons, class role division, guild social features) onto an idle foundation, explicitly avoiding complex heavy-MMO daily task structures.\n- **Claims:** The design targets time-constrained \"pan-users\" and \"fragmented-time users\" who desire MMO social/growth experiences without intensive grinding, positioning the title in a less competitive market niche.\n- **Metrics:** 59.46% year-over-year growth in overseas game business revenue.\n- **Tables/Figures:** References a supporting data visualization/figure (\"如右图所示\") illustrating the game's revenue contribution.\n- **Evidence Types:** Corporate quarterly financial report (《厦门吉比特网络技术股份有限公司2025年第三季度报告》).\n- **Retrieval Questions Answered:** What defines a \"light MMO\" and how does it differ from traditional MMOs and pure idle games? What specific gameplay features does 《杖剑传说》 implement? Who is the target audience? What drove G-bits' Q3 2025 overseas revenue growth? What documentary evidence supports the game's commercial success?"
  },
