    "summary": "This section provides a quantitative analysis of monthly revenue trends and market performance for six mobile game titles, contextualized within a strategic framework of long-term operational patience. **Topics & Claims:** Examines month-by-month financial performance, revenue fluctuation patterns, peak/low identification, stability trends, and cross-game comparisons. Key claims detail distinct performance trajectories: 心动小镇 peaked in July (~29M) before declining; 出发吧麦芬 and 香肠派对 started strong but dropped to negligible levels post-October; 伊瑟 surged in September (17M) and October (30M); 火炬之光：无限 spiked in April (17M) and October (28M); and 仙境传说M maintained stable year-round performance (~1M). **Entities:** 心动小镇, 出发吧麦芬, 伊瑟, 火炬之光：无限, 香肠派对, 仙境传说M. **Dates:** Full calendar year (January–December), with specific analytical focus on January, April, July, September, October, and post-October periods. **Metrics:** Approximate monthly revenue measured in RMB (万元). **Figures & Evidence Types:** Features a line chart visualizing monthly sales/performance and seasonal fluctuations. Data is presented in a structured list/tabular format optimized for time-series querying and direct extraction, sourced from independent research by Diandian Data (点点数据). All financial figures are explicitly noted as approximate."
